            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pins-search-results-group">
          <h3 class="pins-search-results-group-heading">Noise - examining panel meeting agendas</h3>
          <div class="pins-search-results-group-items">
            <ul class="govuk-list">
              <li><a href="#">Agenda for noise, vibration, health and wellbeing hearing (5) - 12 June 2019</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pins-search-results-group">
          <h3 class="pins-search-results-group-heading">Air quality - developer</h3>
